quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  12,21,Misir walon mein say jiss ney ussay khareeda tha uss ney apni biwi say kaha issay boht izzat-o-ehtram kay sath rakho boht mumkin hai kay yeh humen faeeda phonchaye ya issay hum apna beta hi bana len yun to hum ney misir ki sir zamin yousuf ka qadam jama diya kay hum ussay khuwab ki tabeer ka kuch ilm sikha den. Allah apney iraday per ghalib hai lekin aksar log bey ilm hotay hain
  12,22,Aur jab (yousuf) pukhtagi ki umar ko phonch gaye hum ney ussay qooat-e-faisla aur ilm diya hum neko karon ko issi tarah badla detay hain
  12,23,Uss aurat ney jiss kay ghar mein yousuf thay yousuf ko behlana phuslana shuroo kiya kay woh apney nafs ki nigrani chor dey aur darwazay band ker kay kehney lagi lo aajao. Yousuf ney kaha Allah ki panah! Woh mera rab hai mujhay uss ney boht achi tarah rakha hai. Bey insafi kerney walon ka bhala nahi hota
  12,24,Uss aurat ney yousuf ki taraf qasad kiya aur yousuf uss ka qasad kertay agar woh apney perwerdigar ki daleel na dekhtay yun hi hua iss wastay kay hum uss say buraee aur bey hayaee door ker den. Be-shak woh humaray chunay huye bandon mein say tha
  12,25,Dono darwazay ki taraf doray aur uss aurat ney yousuf ka kurta peechay ki taraf say kheench ker phaar dala aur darwazay kay pass hi aurat ka shohar dono ko mill gaya to kehney lagi jo shaks teri biwi kay sath bura irada keray bus uss ki saza yehi hai kay ussay qaid ker diya jaye ya aur koi dard naak saza di jaye
  12,26,Yousuf ney kaha yeh aurat hi mujhay phusla rahi thi aur aurat kay qabeelay hi kay aik shaks ney gawahee di kay agar iss ka kurta aagay say phata hua ho to aurat sachi hai aur yousuf jhoot bolney walon mein say hai
  12,27,Aur agar iss ka kurat peechay ki janib say phaara gaya hai aur aurat jhooti hai aur yousuf sachon mein say hai
  12,28,Khawind ney jo dekha kay yousuf ka kurta peeth ki janob say phaara gaya hai to saaf keh diya kay yeh to tum aurton ki chaal baazi hai be-shak tumhari chaal baazi both bari hai
  12,29,Yousuf abb iss baat ko aati jati kero aur (aey aurat) tu apney gunah say toba ker be-shak tu gunehgaron mein say hai